ActAppropriation Act No. 4, 2012-13
PrecisAppointment of DAVID ANGELL as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Burundi, with residence in Nairobi; RICHARD BALE as Consul General of Canada in Mumbai (Republic of India); STÉPHANE LARUE as Consul General of Canada in Sao Paulo (Federative Republic of Brazil); ALEXANDRE LÉVÊQUE as High Commissioner for Canada in the Republic of Zambia, with residence in Dar-es-Salaam; DOMINIQUE ROSSETTI as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Chad, with residence in Khartoum; and DAVID SPROULE as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Kingdom of Norway.
